## 8.8 生产环境使用

### 8.8.1 安全考虑
```go
// 在生产环境中限制PProf访问
func securePProfHandler() http.HandlerFunc {
    return func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
        // 检查IP白名单
        if !isAllowedIP(r.RemoteAddr) {
            http.Error(w, "Forbidden", http.StatusForbidden)
            return
        }
        
        // 检查认证
        if !isAuthenticated(r) {
            http.Error(w, "Unauthorized", http.StatusUnauthorized)
            return
        }
        
        // 转发到PProf处理器
        pprof.Index(w, r)
    }
}
```

### 8.8.2 性能影响
- CPU分析会降低程序性能约5-10%
- 内存分析影响较小，约1-2%
- 建议在非高峰期进行分析
- 分析完成后及时关闭

### 8.8.3 存储管理
```go
// 自动清理旧的性能分析文件
func cleanupProfiles() {
    ticker := time.NewTicker(24 * time.Hour)
    defer ticker.Stop()
    
    for range ticker.C {
        // 删除7天前的分析文件
        cutoff := time.Now().AddDate(0, 0, -7)
        filepath.Walk("./profiles", func(path string, info os.FileInfo, err error) error {
            if err != nil {
                return err
            }
            
            if !info.IsDir() && info.ModTime().Before(cutoff) {
                os.Remove(path)
            }
            return nil
        })
    }
}
```

## 8.9 集成监控

### 8.9.1 Prometheus集成
```go
// 将PProf指标集成到Prometheus监控
func registerPProfMetrics() {
    // Goroutine数量
    prometheus.NewGaugeFunc(prometheus.GaugeOpts{
        Name: "go_goroutines",
        Help: "Number of goroutines",
    }, func() float64 {
        return float64(runtime.NumGoroutine())
    })
    
    // 内存统计
    prometheus.NewGaugeFunc(prometheus.GaugeOpts{
        Name: "go_memory_heap_alloc_bytes",
        Help: "Heap memory usage in bytes",
    }, func() float64 {
        var m runtime.MemStats
        runtime.ReadMemStats(&m)
        return float64(m.HeapAlloc)
    })
}
```

### 8.9.2 告警规则
```yaml
# Prometheus告警规则
groups:
  - name: pprof_alerts
    rules:
      - alert: HighGoroutineCount
        expr: go_goroutines > 1000
        for: 5m
        labels:
          severity: warning
        annotations:
          summary: "Goroutine数量过多"
          description: "当前Goroutine数量: {{ $value }}"
      
      - alert: HighMemoryUsage
        expr: go_memory_heap_alloc_bytes > 1e9
        for: 5m
        labels:
          severity: warning
        annotations:
          summary: "内存使用过高"
          description: "堆内存使用: {{ $value }} bytes"
```
